---
// ColdStartAnatomy.astro — Cold start breakdown
---
<div class="csa-wrap">
  <h3 class="csa-title">Cold Start — What's Actually Happening</h3>
  <p class="csa-sub">When a new instance spins up from zero, these happen sequentially:</p>
  <div class="csa-timeline">
    <div class="csa-phase csa-p1"><div class="csa-bar" style="--w:10%"></div><span class="csa-lbl">Container Init</span><span class="csa-ms">~50ms</span></div>
    <div class="csa-phase csa-p2"><div class="csa-bar csa-bar--amber" style="--w:25%"></div><span class="csa-lbl">Runtime Bootstrap</span><span class="csa-ms">~200ms</span></div>
    <div class="csa-phase csa-p3"><div class="csa-bar csa-bar--red" style="--w:50%"></div><span class="csa-lbl">Your Code Init</span><span class="csa-ms">~500ms – 3s</span></div>
    <div class="csa-phase csa-p4"><div class="csa-bar csa-bar--green" style="--w:5%"></div><span class="csa-lbl">Handle Request</span><span class="csa-ms">~10ms</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="csa-tips">
    <span class="csa-tips-title">Faster cold starts:</span>
    <div class="csa-tip">Keep deployment packages small (< 50MB)</div>
    <div class="csa-tip">Lazy-load SDK clients — don't init everything at import</div>
    <div class="csa-tip">Use provisioned concurrency for latency-critical paths</div>
    <div class="csa-tip">Choose interpreted runtimes (Node/Python) over compiled (Java/C#)</div>
    <div class="csa-tip">SnapStart (Java) or GraalVM native images eliminate JVM startup</div>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  .csa-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .csa-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 .25rem}.csa-sub{color:#64748b;font-size:.78rem;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .csa-timeline{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
  .csa-phase{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;opacity:0;animation:csaIn .4s ease forwards}
  .csa-p1{animation-delay:.2s}.csa-p2{animation-delay:.4s}.csa-p3{animation-delay:.6s}.csa-p4{animation-delay:.8s}
  @keyframes csaIn{to{opacity:1}}
  .csa-bar{height:20px;background:#06b6d4;border-radius:6px;width:0;animation:csaBar 1s ease forwards;animation-delay:inherit}
  .csa-bar--amber{background:#f59e0b}.csa-bar--red{background:#f87171}.csa-bar--green{background:#4ade80}
  @keyframes csaBar{to{width:var(--w)}}
  .csa-lbl{color:#e2e8f0;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap;min-width:120px}.csa-ms{color:#64748b;font-size:.62rem;font-family:monospace}
  .csa-tips{background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;border:1px solid #334155}
  .csa-tips-title{color:#f59e0b;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;display:block;margin-bottom:6px}
  .csa-tip{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.68rem;line-height:1.7;padding-left:12px;position:relative}.csa-tip::before{content:'→';position:absolute;left:0;color:#4ade80}
</style>
